flowchart LR
    DEV[Developer] --> PR[Pull Request]
    PR --> CI[GitHub Actions CI]

    CI --> FMT[Terraform fmt]
    CI --> VAL[Terraform validate]
    CI --> PLAN[Terraform plan]

    PLAN --> ART[tfplan artifact]
    ART --> REVIEW[Architect Review]

    REVIEW --> APPLY[Manual Apply Approval]
    APPLY --> AWS[AWS Environment]

    AWS --> EVD[Evidence Capture]